text: Kareena Lee (born 16 December 1993) is an Australian swimmer, specialising in open water events. She competed in the women's 10 km event at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships and she finished in 7th place. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Female long-distance swimmers
